reviewText: Words of wisdom...don't talk about if you're not doing it....and if you're doing it, spare us the details and confession...better yet, why are you doing it? You have money and fame, why are you still in the streets? Why are you committing crimes? Why are you bragging? Hip Hop fans will love it. Me, I just love reality and the facts surrounding it. If you don't wanna be labeled a criminal or thug, stop acting like one. If you are not a thug, stop fronting. I went somewhere else with this post, but it was a good documentary!
